text: Carl or Karl Jenkins is the name of: ==Real people== * Carl Elmer Jenkins (born 1926), American Central Intelligence Agency officer, 1952–1973 * Karl Jenkins (born 1944), Welsh musician and composer * Karl Jenkins, American rapper, known professionally as Dice Raw == Characters == * Carl Jenkins, General/Doctor, Minister of Paranormal Warfare in Starship Troopers film * Carl Jenkins (Oz), an inmate of Aryan Brotherhood on the HBO drama Oz
title: Carl Jenkins
